{"tid":1403002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Be water 唔單係指行動上，個腦都要Be water","createTime":"2019-08-03T17:29:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T17:57:01.000Z","uid":293326,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3bdae1ee79384b2f9220ff3984d26103b3ddc3a0","tid":1403002,"uid":293326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:29:02.000Z","msg":"我明白現埸好多勇武好嬲<br />\n聽到左膠講 <br />\n一齊走,一齊走 真係會好撚嬲<br />\n心諗之前犧牲左既義士幾時先救得番<br />\n唔衝唔留守既話點會有用<br />\n請冷靜諗下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但正正係Be water先會救到義士!!</strong></span></span><br />\n呢埸革命係長期作戰<br />\n8月5號罷工係好需要民眾支持<br />\n要挑起市民同警犬既矛盾<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>就要警犬不斷做出擾民既行動</strong></span></span><br />\n令本來既淺藍,中年人例戈<br />\n馬鞍山就係好好既例子<br />\n事實上後尾馬鞍山居民都做埋前線<br />\n希望各位勇武可以 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不送頭</strong></span></span>既情況下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不斷做, 日日做</strong></span></span><br />\n逼使警犬使用武力擾民,同時全身而退, 為下次運動做準備<br />\n唔好比警犬既行為令憤怒衝昏頭腦<br />\n送頭不單會增加淨低勇武既負擔, 仲會令我地失走作戰既持久性<br />\n我地既目標:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>長期罷工,逼政府回應所有訴求</strong></span></span><br />\n呢個目標需要好多社區既市民配合<br />\nBTW 無論如何,尊重前線決定"},{"pid":"fe09553c67686ded8d72910636a90548f3ad3ae1","tid":1403002,"uid":293326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2982ecef89baa4da13f5e475bd7d546aeb66f7a","tid":1403002,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:29:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"28a79eb0b232ede5efb41f797c106cce75ad1739","tid":1403002,"uid":293326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bad8683923df7281362f902cf6f491125e0b36b","tid":1403002,"uid":293326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59f5ea6aed6018620b3568da77555bdcdabbb93","tid":1403002,"uid":293326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465fd3c206e178acec97236dc36438d62374a8df","tid":1403002,"uid":293326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:31:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ee2771ec5a6fe13ec995b63f4d9